#: ui/main.qml:26
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Time-based features such as Night Light and dynamic wallpapers can be "
"synchronized with the day-night cycle. Choose your preferred cycle here."
msgstr ""
"Night Light やダイナミック壁紙などの時間ベースの機能は、昼夜サイクルと同期さ"
"せることができます。お好みのサイクルを設定してください。"

#: ui/main.qml:42
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@label:listbox part of a sentence: 'Determine sunrise and sunset times "
"[based on]'"
msgid "Determine sunrise and sunset times:"
msgstr "日の出と日の入りの時間:"

#: ui/main.qml:47
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@item:inlistbox part of a sentence: 'Determine sunrise and sunset times'"
msgid "Based on device's location"
msgstr "デバイスの地域に基づく"

#: ui/main.qml:48
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@item:inlistbox part of a sentence: 'Determine sunrise and sunset times'"
msgid "Using custom times"
msgstr "カスタム設定"

#: ui/main.qml:60
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Sunrise:"
msgstr "日の出:"

#: ui/main.qml:75
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Sunset:"
msgstr "日の入り:"

#: ui/main.qml:89
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:spinbox"
msgid "Transition duration:"
msgstr "日の出/日の入りにかかる時間:"

#: ui/main.qml:95
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@item:valuesuffix transition duration"
msgid "%1 minute"
msgid_plural "%1 minutes"
msgstr[0] "%1 分"

#: ui/main.qml:118
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio"
msgid "Automatically detect location"
msgstr "自動で地域を識別"

#: ui/main.qml:145
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The <application>GeoClue2</application> service will be used to periodically "
"update the device's location using GPS or cell tower triangulation if "
"available, or else by sending its IP address to <link url='https://geoip.com/"
"privacy/'>GeoIP</link>."
msgstr ""
"利用可能な場合は GPS やジオロケーションを利用して定期的にデバイスの位置を特定"
"するため、<application>GeoClue2</application> サービスを使用します。GPS やジ"
"オロケーションが利用できない場合は <link url='https://geoip.com/"
"privacy/'>GeoIP</link> に IP アドレスを送信して特定します。"

#: ui/main.qml:146
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"The <application>%1</application> service will be used to periodically "
"update the device's location. Please open a bug report at <link url='https://"
"bugs.kde.org'>https://bugs.kde.org</link> asking KDE developers to write a "
"detailed description of what this service will do."
msgstr ""
"定期的にデバイスの位置を特定するため、<application>%1</application> サービス"
"が使用されます。<link url='https://bugs.kde.org'>https://bugs.kde.org</link> "
"でこのサービスが何をするのかについての説明を記載するよう KDE の開発者にお問い"
"合わせください。"

#: ui/main.qml:163
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:radio"
msgid "Use manual location:"
msgstr "手動で設定:"

#: ui/main.qml:175
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Latitude:"
msgstr "緯度:"

#: ui/main.qml:195
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Longitude:"
msgstr "経度:"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:52
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip; the variables are times of day, e.g. 07:30"
msgid "Sunrise starts at %1 and ends at %2"
msgstr "日の出の開始時刻は %1, 終了時刻は %2 です"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:57
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Sunrise"
msgstr "日の出"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:77
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip; the variables are times of day, e.g. 07:30"
msgid "Sunset starts at %1 and ends at %2"
msgstr "日の入りの開始時刻は %1, 終了時刻は %2 です"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:82
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label"
msgid "Sunset"
msgstr "日の入り"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:107
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Sunrise and sunset times cannot be determined at your location due to polar "
"day. Choose custom times instead."
msgstr ""
"極日のため、お住まいの地域では日の出と日の入りの時刻を特定できません。代わり"
"にカスタム時刻を選択してください。"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:109
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Sunrise and sunset times cannot be determined at your location due to polar "
"night. Choose custom times instead."
msgstr ""
"極夜のため、お住まいの地域では日の出と日の入りの時刻を特定できません。代わり"
"にカスタム時刻を選択してください。"

#: ui/SunPath.qml:111
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Sunrise and sunset times cannot be reliably determined at your location. "
"Choose custom times instead."
msgstr ""
"お住まいの地域では、日の出と日の入りの時刻を正確に特定することができません。"
"代わりにカスタム時刻を選択してください。"

#: ui/TimeField.qml:31
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Time separator between hours and minutes"
msgid ":"
msgstr ":"

#: ui/WorldMap.qml:76
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@label:chooser Tap should be translated to mean touching using a touchscreen"
msgid "Tap to choose your location on the map."
msgstr "地図をタップしてお住まいの地域を選択してください。"

#: ui/WorldMap.qml:77
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@label:chooser Click should be translated to mean clicking using a mouse"
msgid "Click to choose your location on the map."
msgstr "地図をクリックしてお住まいの地域を選択してください。"

#: ui/WorldMap.qml:189
#, kde-format
msgid "Zoom in"
msgstr "拡大"

#: ui/WorldMap.qml:206
#, kde-format
msgid "Zoom out"
msgstr "縮小"

